# ⚠️ S44 PROTECTIONS:
# - DO NOT change --glass-* token values (opacity, blur, shadow, border)
# - DO NOT change glass-input pulse animation timing (4s) or keyframes
# - DO NOT change rainbow-glow-pulse animation (12s, hue rotation)
# - DO NOT change object-badge-dot-pulse animation
# - DO NOT modify .glass-glow ::before inset/blur values
# - Light vs dark token differences are INTENTIONAL — don't "normalize"
# - --glass-transition: 280ms is deliberate — not 200 or 300
# Improvements should be ADDITIVE: new spacing, new shadows, NOT replacing S44 values

###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Apply ONLY the small (S) improvements identified in T9 trend audit.
One change at a time. Build after each. No regressions.

###############################################################################
# EXECUTION RULES
###############################################################################
rules:
  - Implement ONE improvement at a time
  - Verify build passes after each change
  - Check both light AND dark mode after each change
  - If visual result is worse, revert immediately
  - No new npm packages
  - No changes to component APIs
  - Only CSS tokens, className adjustments, and minor JSX tweaks

###############################################################################
# LIKELY IMPROVEMENTS (to be confirmed by T9 audit)
###############################################################################

### Category: Spacing & Layout
  1. Normalize horizontal padding across screens (px-4 everywhere)
  2. Normalize section spacing (mb-5 or mb-6, pick one)
  3. Increase padding inside glass containers (if < 16px)
  4. Ensure 8px grid alignment (gap-2, gap-3, gap-4 consistently)

### Category: Typography
  5. Review font-weight hierarchy (semibold for headings, medium for labels, regular for body)
  6. Ensure caption text ≥ 12px (text-xs = 12px — verify)
  7. Add letter-spacing to all-caps text (if any exists)

### Category: Corners
  8. Normalize border-radius: cards = rounded-2xl, buttons = rounded-xl, chips = rounded-full
  9. Ensure bottom sheet corners consistent (rounded-2xl already — verify)

### Category: Shadows & Depth
  10. Review glass shadow depth (subtle but visible)
  11. Ensure cards have soft shadow (not hard edge)
  12. Add subtle shadow to bottom nav bar

### Category: Colors
  13. Review text-muted-foreground opacity (not too dim, not too bright)
  14. Review active/selected state prominence
  15. Ensure destructive color is clearly red (not some ambiguous shade)

### Category: Component Polish
  16. Add subtle scale effect on button press (active:scale-[0.98])
  17. Smooth out transition durations (consistent 200ms or 250ms)
  18. Icon stroke width consistency (1.5 or 2, not mixed)

###############################################################################
